overview.en: BOXFIVE is a project dedicated to creating more convenient and convenient services for consumers and members. It provides a variety of services for a large number of users of the BOXFIVE business complex and the users of other joint businesses through the implementation of consumer payment, preferential purchase, and currency exchange.
overview.zh: BOXFIVE是一个致力于为消费者、会员创造更优惠、便捷服务的项目。它通过实现消费支付、优惠买单、代币兑换等线上线下使用场景，为BOXFIVE商业综合体的大量用户，及其他联合商家的用户，提供多样化的服务，并实现各商家之间的积分兑换流通。
